query:
UPDATE events SET 
  coverImageUrl = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470229722913-7c0e2dbbafd3?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 2 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514525253161-7a46d19cd819?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 30001 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571266028243-e4733b0f0bb0?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 30002 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516450360452-9312f5e86fc7?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 30003 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574391884720-bbc3740c59d1?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60001 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533174072545-7a4b6ad7a6c3?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60002 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60003 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537996194471-e657df975ab4?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60004 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547826039-bfc35e0f1ea8?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60005 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518998053901-5348d3961a04?w=1920&q=80'
    WHEN 60006 THEN 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1429962714451-bb934ecdc4ec?w=1920&q=80'
    ELSE coverImageUrl
  END,
  tagline = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 'When the city sleeps, we gather'
    WHEN 2 THEN 'Your first step into the unknown'
    WHEN 30001 THEN 'A night of dark revelations'
    WHEN 30002 THEN 'The beginning of something new'
    WHEN 30003 THEN 'Where legends are born'
    WHEN 60001 THEN 'Feel the bass in your bones'
    WHEN 60002 THEN 'Fine dining for the elite'
    WHEN 60003 THEN 'Escape to paradise'
    WHEN 60004 THEN 'Where art meets the streets'
    WHEN 60005 THEN 'Discover our hidden treasures'
    WHEN 60006 THEN 'Above the city lights'
    ELSE tagline
  END,
  title = CASE id
    WHEN 30001 THEN 'THE HANGING'
    WHEN 30002 THEN 'THE LAUNCH'
    WHEN 30003 THEN 'GENESIS'
    ELSE title
  END,
  featuredOrder = CASE id
    WHEN 1 THEN 8
    WHEN 2 THEN 7
    WHEN 60001 THEN 6
    WHEN 60006 THEN 5
    WHEN 60002 THEN 4
    WHEN 60003 THEN 3
    WHEN 60004 THEN 2
    WHEN 60005 THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END;
